otto available commands: 
	!away -- display current away message
	!idle -- give idle time information (precise idle time up to 15 minutes)
	!gag -- disable auto-replying with away messages
	!ungag -- re-enable auto-replying with away messages
	!listen -- Start receiving notification messages
	!listen1 -- Receive the next notification messages
	!unlisten -- Stop receiving notification messages
	!joke -- tell a joke
	!help -- display this message
Notes: 
	-- otto will autorespond to any message at most once every 900 seconds with the current away message if there is one (unless gagged).  
	-- If not idle but currently marked away, this shall indicate uninterruptable work time during which I do not check messages
